metadata.name: Cris Cray Music Collection Pass
metadata.description: Cris Cray Music Subscription or CC1 NFT is a Complete Collection of 40+ music NFTs. This collection of 555 (only) Subscription Passes comes with music (EP), anthem songs (audio files), custom “Cover Art” works created for sixteen exclusively selected NFT community projects. Four different Music Artist will create 24 unique unreleased exclusive music creations all in NFT format. Evolving with each milestone (3-4 music NFT completions). You get 42+ evolving graphics, one for each of the NFT songs, (cover art), a CC1 Holder Finalized Graphic and thank you contract for long term holders who would like to continue their Spiritual journey, after February 2023 when this project completes. See our website for full details on how to claim your merchandise, register for free NFT drops, access L2E, IRL services and more, via Google form. XOXO Cray FAM!
